ArtyTorrent Pack 70-Electro Drum Loops 130-139bpm-WAV
-----------------------------------------------------

A pack of electro beat loops. These are mostly TR-808 and 909-style loops in an old skool style, but there are some 4/4 loops for modern electro house tracks.
Tempo ranges from 130-139 bpm.

Torrent contains 9 RAR files with 171 loops
-------------------------------------------
Chicago Fire Electro 130-138 (14 loops)
Dist 909 loops 130 (6 loops)
Ghetto Electro 130-138 (22 loops)
Machine Language Drum 130-139 (15 loops)
Machine Language Strange 130-139 (19 loops)
Magix Electro 130 (12 loops)
Misc Electro 130-139 (58 loops)
Robotic 130 (10 loops)
SF Electro 130 (15 loops)

Samples are from a variety of sources including CDs by EastWest, Sony/Sonic Foundry, Magix, Loopology/Syntrillium, and Tekniks, and have all been normalized and acidized as 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz. Approx tempo is included in each filename.
